    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要一个饼图来展示学生全年的概念学习进度。总共18个概念，包括已完成的课程。我想分成几个状态：已经学过的、正在学的、还没学的，以及复习过的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "Notions Vues",
        "Notions en cours",
        "Notions futures",
        "Notions révisées"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。四个类别：已学、在学、未学、已复习。确认一下数据：已学2个，在学6个，未学10个，复习0个？这样加起来是18个概念。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Notions Vues",
        "Notions en cours",
        "Notions futures",
        "Notions révisées"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，数字没错。标题用\"-- Progression d'année au niveau des notions\"，强调这是年度概念进度。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先用默认主题配置，把四个扇区画出来。已学占2份，在学6份，未学10份，复习暂时是0。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "theme",
        "Notions Vues",
        "Notions en cours",
        "Notions futures",
        "Notions révisées"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，复习是0的话，那个扇区会显示吗？还是直接隐藏？我希望保留这个类别，即使现在没有数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Notions révisées"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "会显示的，Mermaid的饼图会把0值也渲染出来，只是没有面积。这样以后有复习数据时可以直接更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Notions révisées"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以。另外注意前三类的总和必须是18，因为\"Notions Vues\"、\"Notions en cours\"、\"Notions futures\"这三个涵盖了全部概念，复习是额外的重复计数。",
      "elements_involved": [
